README FILE

Generate a streaming source for gps coordinates
generate a program to query for the cordinates from the streaming source
parse the streamed data to a file to get the final longitude and latitude

streaming source ----- source.php
application received the gps and decode them  ----- application.php


How to Run ...
Linux
Running on a terminal
create a directory and add the files to the directory
to run execute php application.php

note ... you should have php installed in your machine

The system will output on the terminal a json encoded response and write to a file called coordinates.log

To view the output on the coordinates.log file, tail the file i.e. tail -f coordinates.log

